text: phir bhee unhonne use jhuthala diya, to hamane use aur jo naav mein usake saath (savaar) the, bacha liya aur unheen ko unaka uttaraadhikaaree bana diya aur unhen jalamagan kar diya, jinhonne hamaaree nishaaniyon ko jhuthala diya. atah dekhalo ki unaka parinaam kiya hua, jo sachet kiye gaye the
